# Root-owned adapter secrets for ChefGroep company-control shadow.
# Populate only company-scope credentials. Do NOT copy UDO fleet paths or
# utrecht_kater extensions secrets here.
#
# Adapters fail-closed until the corresponding names are set (values never logged):
# GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN
# LINEAR_API_KEY
# CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID
# CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN
# EXA_API_KEY
# FIRECRAWL_API_KEY
# HF_TOKEN
# BRAVE_API_KEY
# RESEND_API_KEY
# NOTION_API_KEY
# SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN
# UPSTASH_EMAIL
# UPSTASH_API_KEY
